{"tid":2435330,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"專家組：死者有血壓高﹑血脂高  現時並沒有數據顯示接種科興疫苗後會誘發中風","createTime":"2021-03-06T07:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T07:39:32.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5193b920be1c4ef624978c7443286b5758eeef60","tid":2435330,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:13:15.000Z","msg":"新冠疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會召集人孔繁毅教授今日（6日）接種復必泰疫苗，對被問到再有個案接種疫苗後死亡，他表示有關個案仍要委員會討論，同時要等待臨床9數據分析，包括解剖後情況，才知道其個案情況。<br />\n<br />\n孔繁毅指出初步了解，該名55歲女有血壓高﹑血脂高而中風，下周一會開會審視個案，現時並沒有數據顯示接種科興疫苗後會誘發中風，強調長期病患者如果情況控制得好，可以接種疫苗，問題是血壓、糖尿控制不好，接種疫苗前就要先諮詢醫生。"},{"pid":"0eeba5cc9a30355ab21ee24780a79e2442c89eec","tid":2435330,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b380ae775908c98de2acaee6b8099b41c4dce8c1","tid":2435330,"uid":19557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:14:16.000Z","msg":"唔駛講咁多喇<br />\n一係緊張<br />\n一係冇食早餐"},{"pid":"b15afd94a9749b3d4a8bfc745b09be03a4055569","tid":2435330,"uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-prod.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/incoming/article15627845.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200/1_CO_MEN_030119BALL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.manchestereveningnews.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle15627845.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs1200%2F1_CO_MEN_030119BALL.jpg&h=3b920078&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b650b257a3bb34bbdd25200ab346fb9f172568ab","tid":2435330,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"打咁多字把撚咩<br />\n八個字總結：廢老抵死,關我撚事"},{"pid":"5b1424d84353a